===Pronunciation===
*[[w:AHD|AHD]]: /ā/
*[[w:IPA|IPA]]: /eɪ/
*[[w:SAMPA|SAMPA]]: /eI/

===Interjection===
'''eh'''
#('''eh?''') Used as a [[tag question]], to emphasise what goes before or to request that the listener confirm or agree with what has been said.
<!--other definitions?-->
#:''So what time shall we meet, eh?''
#:''These hot dogs are really good, eh?''

===={{usage}}====
This is a predominantly [[Canadian]] term; using it outside of [[Canada]] often conveys that you are trying to sound (sarcastically) Canadian, or even French-Canadian.

